            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-706016f918bded4e-f09fcd twpub-706016f918bded4e-6b4cd0\"><p>Project Gutenberg-tm is synonymous with the free distribution of\nelectronic works in formats readable by the widest variety of\ncomputers including obsolete, old, middle-aged and new computers. It\nexists because of the efforts of hundreds of volunteers and donations\nfrom people in all walks of life.</p></div>"
