            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/706016f918bded4e/text/000002336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-706016f918bded4e-f09fcd twpub-706016f918bded4e-6b4cd0\"><p>The Project Gutenberg Literary Archive Foundation is a non profit\n501(c)(3) educational corporation organized under the laws of the\nstate of Mississippi and granted tax exempt status by the Internal\nRevenue Service. The Foundation's EIN or federal tax identification\nnumber is 64-6221541. Contributions to the Project Gutenberg Literary\nArchive Foundation are tax deductible to the full extent permitted by\nU.S. federal laws and your state's laws.</p></div>"
        },
