            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-706016f918bded4e-f09fcd twpub-706016f918bded4e-6b4cd0\"><h5>Section 4. Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h5></div>"
