            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/706016f918bded4e/text/000002344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-706016f918bded4e-f09fcd twpub-706016f918bded4e-6b4cd0\"><p>International donations are gratefully accepted, but we cannot make\nany statements concerning tax treatment of donations received from\noutside the United States. U.S. laws alone swamp our small staff.</p></div>"
