            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-706016f918bded4e-f09fcd twpub-706016f918bded4e-6b4cd0\"><p>Please check the Project Gutenberg Web pages for current donation\nmethods and addresses. Donations are accepted in a number of other\nways including checks, online payments and credit card donations. To\ndonate, please visit: www.gutenberg.org/donate</p></div>"
